An SZ troll is not a small schoolchild.  Small schoolchildren are different in that they have the potential to become productive members of society and may, at some point in the future, engage in intelligent discussion or debate, or be remotely helpful to someone at some point in their lives.  Serant has no such potential.  It is far, far lower on the evolutionary scale than a small schoolchild.<br>
<br>
